  "description": "Infinite inventory and stack size!",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #aa00aa; font-size: 24px; font-family: 'trebuchet ms', geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/104cae1f14fd5ccf1da2154855438401.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"644\" height=\"134\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #aa00aa; font-family: 'trebuchet ms', geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ol1Tcf8.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"67\" /></strong></span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #aa00aa; font-size: 24px; font-family: 'trebuchet ms', geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong>Infinite inventory and stack size!</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Inventory sorting&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff00ff; font-size: 24px;\">&diams;</span>&nbsp;Infinitely expanding Inventory</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff00ff; font-size: 24px;\">&diams;</span>&nbsp;Infinite stack size</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"text-align: center;\" src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/2448b3def066e4d05f6b0447a40fb8fe.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"228\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>This mod allows items in your inventory to stack infinitely and automatically expands your inventory when it fills up! You can even sort your inventory by name, quantity, or ID! You'll never have to worry about your inventory filling up or having to build a storage room ever again!&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/397/566/infinite-stack-size.png\" width=\"900\" height=\"203\" /><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #333333;\"><em>Infinite stack size (configurable)</em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #333333;\"><em><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/397/567/inventory-sorting.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"514\" />Sort your inventory by Name, Quantity, or ID</em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #333333;\"><em><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/397/568/infinitely-expanding.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"717\" />Infinitely expands your inventory as it fills up (configurable)</em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #333333;\"><em><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/furgl_and_2piradians\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/g2vJewK.png\" alt=\"Patreon\" width=\"300\" height=\"70\" /></a><a href=\"https://discord.gg/eUpvRXJSgD\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/cbfIsqM.png\" alt=\"Discord\" width=\"219\" height=\"70\" /></a></em></span></p>",
